Run ADE planning phases (Intent + Research + Plan) for: $ARGUMENTS

Follow Phases 0-2 of the ADE workflow:
1. Extract intent (type, goal, acceptance criteria, scope)
2. Research the codebase (up to 3 parallel Explore agents)
3. Present findings and get user approval (USER GATE)
4. Write implementation plan to `.ade/tasks/<task-id>/plan.md`
5. Verify plan completeness (PLAN GATE)

Save all artifacts to `.ade/tasks/<task-id>/`.
Update `.ade/tasks/<task-id>/status.md` at each phase transition.
